total of 12 residents, discover 66 combinations of couples with unique storylines!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/d88659541a3533cdce8584ccd0b64639.poster.avif?t=1764037337\" width=700 height=700 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/d88659541a3533cdce8584ccd0b64639.webm?t=1764037337\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1789490/extras/d88659541a3533cdce8584ccd0b64639.mp4?t=1764037337\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♥ <strong>Take your matchmaking to the next level</strong> - unlock minigames, manor upgrades, ghostie hats, and more! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >♥ <strong>New Game+</strong> - not done matchmaking? The memories board retains the dates and relationship talks you’ve unlocked from previous runs. Other New Game+ features help you progress relationships faster!</p>",
